## 3. Scale Estimation

| Metric | Estimate |
|---|---|
| Daily Active Users | 500M |
| Ad impressions per day | 10B |
| Avg candidates scored per request | 100–500 ads |
| Peak QPS (queries per second) | ~500K–1M |
| Training data size (30 days) | ~500B rows (after downsampling) |
| Click rate (positive label rate) | 1–5% → heavily imbalanced |
| Feature store read latency required | < 10ms |

