## 9. Feedback Loop & Online Learning

```
Ad served → user clicks or doesn't
        ↓
Event streamed via Kafka
        ↓
Flink streaming job joins click events with impression events (within 30s window)
        ↓
Labeled training example written to data lake (S3)
        ↓
Feeds daily batch retrain + optional real-time feature updates
```

**Challenge — Feedback delay:** A user might click an ad 10 minutes after seeing it. Solution: hold a join window (e.g., up to 1 hour) before finalizing the label for recent impressions.

**Challenge — Position bias:** Ads shown in higher positions get more clicks regardless of true relevance. Handle with **position feature** during training, and **dropout of position at serving time** (set position=0 or use a separate debiasing model).

